></blockquote><br />\n起碼佢地賣屎你食都會整到唔似屎嘅野出嚟<br />\n香港m記擺到明就係賣屎畀你食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954fe942be8f8463c6708ab3f3da725f57899c7a","tid":336603,"uid":125208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食材問題，日本連吉野家都係極品<br />\n係香港既先咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本M記未又係福喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地會檢討，好多間執左，諗辦法挽回你信心<br />\n香港？你鍾意食呀？開多幾間，整個18件過你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeaa64f904a8d8b3a77481b7e30cad7f213f2fb","tid":336603,"uid":121240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"日本m記有qoo飲 仲要用中杯裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3998511d78310a5500711ab86a6c02eeb2788401","tid":336603,"uid":129043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"香港啲包走晒樣 見到都唔想食"},{"pid":"aa77e504466bab6bbf686a242f505109fa5abf7b","tid":336603,"uid":71789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"薯條可以轉4件麥樂雞㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a82fb2353c30d317e0e4b273890aaee3e2c370","tid":336603,"uid":123103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>薯條可以轉4件麥樂雞㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n5件，一陣再吃"},{"pid":"8b6dd5ffce6cb7381800ebcb27a060b597fffe88","tid":336603,"uid":29684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"以為係窮人唔好生仔巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e435b058